  "markup": "Americans spend at least $50 billion each year on back pain, and that\u0026rsquo;s just for the more easily identified costs.\nOver 31 million Americans experience LBP at any given time.  One-half of all working Americans admit to having back pain symptoms each year, and LBP is the second most common reason for visits to the doctor\u0026rsquo;s office, and is outnumbered only by upper-respiratory infections. Back pain is one of the most common reasons for missed work.\nIn this webinar we will work to unravel lower back pain (LBP) from a new perspective and discuss how to add Super Pulsed Laser (SPL) to your clinical approach for superior outcomes.  SPL can be blended with a multitude of techniques and practices.\nJoin Dr. Chris Carraway and he discusses Alleviating Low Back Pain with super pulsed laser"
}]]></Value>
